game.name: Cyber Truck Drive Simulator
game.description:
This time you have got a chance to drive on the surface of Mars! Is not pretty exciting and challenging? If yes, join Cyber Truck Drive Simulator and gear up to enjoy a unique driving experience. Everyone on the internet is talking about this brand-new racing challenge. Where are you, friends? Select your car, fasten your seat and get ready to ride the wonderful car models to complete several important missions! Remember you have only a limited time to get your job done. So try to be a bit fast.

Your objective in this one of the best car games is to grab the flags using the map to avoid damage to your car. Make sure that the damage and loss to your car are very minimal. Hurry up boys since the clock is running very fast! The realistic graphics, awesome physics, fabulous sound effects, cool car models, and the advanced interface will be enough to keep you engrossed for hours. Find out the hidden flags as fast as you can to complete each level with the maximum possible score!

Choose the free mode to play and be prepared to drive around and allow yourself to check out the game physics! It will be great fun when you control a unique car from Tesla. You can also change the camera view anytime to keep your eyes on your vehicle from all sides. Find the real objective of your journey by following the arrow showing on the screen in this cool physics game! Good luck to improve your driving pleasure from the multiple camera angles and have fun without download!
